Criterion Capital Management






Overview
Established in September 2002, Criterion Capital Management, LLC (Criterion) is a San Francisco-based investment adviser registered with the Securities and Exchange Commission. Criterion's investment strategies seek to generate compelling, risk adjusted returns.
Chris Lord, David Riley, Tomoko Fortune and Louis Chang bring a combined 55+ years of investing experience in the global technology, media and telecommunications (TMT) sectors with varying backgrounds, complementary investing skills and proven stock selection ability, both long and short, in this broad universe of companies.



