Firm Overview
Criterion Capital Management is an independent wealth management firm based in Nashville, Tennessee. We serve a select group of individuals, families, businesses, and foundations helping them build, manage, preserve, and transfer wealth. 
Our custom tailored wealth management strategies include portfolio management, retirement planning, education planning, risk management strategies, as well as assistance with estate investment planning.
Our principals have more than 50 years of combined financial and investment experience and our clients tell us one of the greatest benefits they receive is knowing they have a dynamic plan in place, which is being actively monitored by experienced, trustworthy advisors. 
 
 













