Criterion Capital Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 6:28 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Criterion Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Criterion Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm provides its services to pooled investment vehicles and institutional investors. It also launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It employs a long and short equity strategy to make its investments. The firm primarily focuses on investment in companies in the technology sector including software, internet, networking, wireless, and hardware. It employs a fundamental analysis to create its portfolios. Criterion Capital Management, LLC was founded in September 2002 and is based in San Francisco, California.


